<!--[if lte IE 9]>
<script type="text/javascript" >
    
$(document).ready(function() {        
    function showHideElem(watch){
        var elem = $(watch);
        if(elem.css("display") === "none"){
            elem.css("display","block");

        } else if (elem.css("display") === "block") {
            elem.css("display","none");
        }
    }

    
    $("#handle-dp").on('click', function(){
        showHideElem('.watch-dp');
    });

    
    $("#handle-tr").on('click', function(){
        showHideElem('.watch-tr');
    });

    
    $("#handle-op").on('click', function(){
        showHideElem('.watch-op');
    });    
});


</script>  

<![endif]-->
